{"tid":723412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"忌妒哥哥交女友　14歲少女割喉殺人","createTime":"2018-06-30T11:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T07:38:57.000Z","uid":86587,"like":519,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"34029ac96ebe150dc79515b7606179528223dc63","tid":723412,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:19:58.000Z","msg":"美國一名14歲女孩，因為妒忌哥哥的女友，於是趁深夜潛入她的房間，用破碗碎片將她割喉，還自稱是變態殺人狂，一直想開殺戒。 <br />\n<br />\n家住威斯康辛州新里奇蒙的布基（Kali J. Bookey），因為哥哥交了15歲的女友後變得開朗，讓她感到忌妒。她日前得知，被害者的母親要外出三天，只剩哥哥女友一人顧家，於是在周三（27日）凌晨約4時，騎腳踏車到17.7公里外，潛入被害人的臥室。 <br />\n<br />\n被害人表示，布基掩住她的嘴巴，先用拳頭痛擊她的臉數下，再拿兩個碗敲打她的頭，然後用碎片慢慢割開她喉嚨。布基問被害人，想馬上就死個痛快還是慢慢流血到死，被害人選擇慢慢死後，布基就停止割她。布基臨走時說，她是變態殺人狂，一直想開殺戒，很可能會再殺人，然後祝哥哥女友「來世愉快」。 <br />\n<br />\n布基周三犯案後還自行報警，表示深夜騎腳踏車時，有兩名蒙面男人持刀想綁架她，她被迫透露哥哥的女友獨留在家，他們應該綁架她而不是自己。 <br />\n<br />\n警方獲報後，趕到被害人的旅行車房子內調查，發現被害人頸部嚴重出血，但一息尚存，仍可向警方講出真相。<br />\n<br />\n布基被捕後表示，並非真的想殺死哥哥的女友，只是嚇她離開當地，這樣哥哥就會更親近家人。她又表示已策劃襲擊好幾個星期。布基被控一級意圖謀殺，不准保釋。受害人則因 傷勢嚴重，仍在醫院接受治療。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20160730/640_ab692701d4a18d63cbfc05aa1dc7358c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20160730%2F640_ab692701d4a18d63cbfc05aa1dc7358c.jpg&h=4126df23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n病嬌兄控大好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b895ceb6935bf36e68ee2a2b7596071e01c4db","tid":723412,"uid":62318,"like":73,"dislike":3,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:21:46.000Z","msg":"我有講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10c626c29fa7378e4b8db145fc319a3d4198951","tid":723412,"uid":121546,"like":75,"dislike":2,"score":73,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:22:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cl67Hli6A00\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fcl67Hli6A00&d=Clv51i9CFE68NckJGaYwZ%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=92a57364\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cl67Hli6A00</a><br />\n依個女仔大個應該會係咁"},{"pid":"d2444f89b46c682269a5d96a4c16db9edf0f09fa","tid":723412,"uid":59898,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e587f0773d977f9f0bef83824b0c0921483700b7","tid":723412,"uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":114,"score":-103,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:23:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>受害人則因 傷勢嚴重，仍在醫院接受治療。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都未死... 殺乜野人?"},{"pid":"02f50714aab1d36b776ee108277a8c2573071550","tid":723412,"uid":175523,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:24:10.000Z","msg":"鬼妹真係快大"},{"pid":"e060c3e6ac6ef8fba1948d89ecd47e66e5f6b3ad","tid":723412,"uid":45477,"like":21,"dislike":9,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:27:29.000Z","msg":"快點割我喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec687f09f5b97a2b6c3e6b85efc1aabe7cb657f3","tid":723412,"uid":41818,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:29:56.000Z","msg":"兄控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89d880770e8540a685057305d21d037eb0f0fe1","tid":723412,"uid":50779,"like":174,"dislike":5,"score":169,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:30:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d298cf12685b5b081a81d8e4a7ef4341404bf82","tid":723412,"uid":123264,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:33:15.000Z","msg":"病嬌<br />\n妹調教日記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82eb2b1be9528946d2baecd51b3f2459b43e0c33","tid":723412,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b10c626c29fa7378e4b8db145fc319a3d41